{
  "info": {
    "name": "OmniFlow AI API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for OmniFlow AI backend\n\n## Setup\n1. Set `baseUrl` variable to `https://omniflow-ai.onrender.com`\n2. For demo mode (no Firebase): Set `DEMO_MODE=true` in server/.env\n3. For Firebase: set `token` variable with a valid Firebase ID token\n\n## Demo Mode\nWhen Firebase is not configured, all endpoints work with in-memory mock data.\nAuth endpoints accept any email/password and return a fake token.\nUse `Bearer demo-token-123` in Auth header.",
